arket and entrepreneurship programs|journal=World Bank Development Impact Evaluation (DIME)|date=2015|ref=harv}} *{{cite book |last1=Collier |first1=Paul |authorlink1=Paul Collier |first2=Anke |last2=Hoeffler |year=2002 |title=Greed and Grievance in Civil War |url=http://www-wds.worldbank.org/servlet/WDSContentServer/WDSP/IB/2000/06/17/000094946_00060205420011/Rendered/PDF/multi_page.pdf |series=The World Bank Policy Research Working Paper |volume=2355 |ref=harv}} {{refend}}
